{"tid":1530703,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"左派深紅學校罷課，學校要求學生除校服！","createTime":"2019-09-02T04:36:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-02T04:56:08.000Z","uid":145381,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"63e991a9f1c4fdf95a79fed8119a3cafd4ee4bc0","tid":1530703,"uid":145381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T04:36:46.000Z","msg":"今日左派深紅學校，香港教育工作者聯會黃楚標中學出現學生罷課，亦有舊生到場聲援。<br />\n早上八時，罷課學生聚集校門內，期間一名訓導主任指罵罷課學生，並多次要求罷課學生停止罷課及要求舊生離開。<br />\n舊生及罷課學生沒有理會，繼續留守。後來，舊生在門外高叫口號時，遭到市民作出挑釁。<br />\n之後有市民報警要求警察驅趕在場聲援的舊生，警察到場後表示並無理由驅趕。<br />\n<br />\n更新：12:15 學生放學，舊生及學生在門外叫口號，學校老師要求學生不能穿着校服叫口號及表達立場，理由是不能代表學校，學生被迫脫去校服表達訴求。<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xEgy2tj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxEgy2tj.jpg&h=75edae4d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8YOake0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8YOake0.jpg&h=2abddaab&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/09/02/123618_db165426e894c607611c853c9332c8e2.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F09%2F02%2F123618_db165426e894c607611c853c9332c8e2.jpeg&h=e9fab77e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iQiUMVc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiQiUMVc.jpg&h=2b531e0e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gpR3Ffd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgpR3Ffd.jpg&h=8fee25b3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c89e2d90ba259d0c19a8219c0c17d21e0342b691","tid":1530703,"uid":266362,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T04:40:01.000Z","msg":"跪求<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/